Essentially, there are two factions working toward the same goals... both want all of Norrath under their control. You have the lawfully good army of Zenten on one side and the Gouka Empire - built by Neudal, servant of Innoruuk, on the other. As the last remaining member of the old Combine Empire, Kal`Navae has vowed to protect the land and make sure such a calamity never happens again. The Combine Empire was an incredible spectacle with magicks and technologies beyond what many could imagine. It was the arrogance and lack of responsibility that caused the Empire to eventually crumble. Knowing this, Kal`Navae has made it her mission to keep all potential threats at bay. She realizes that should the Zenten or Gouka ever win the war, corruption and potential disaster will fall upon Norrath. History has an odd way of repeating itself and she has taken it upon herself to make sure this does not happen.<br>
<br>
